{"title":"Tour de Frankie Must See: Paola Berber’s 3rd Ride of Mexico’s Hardest Ultracycling Event","link":"https://bikerumor.com/tour-de-frankie-must-see-paola-berbers-3rd-ride-of-mexicos-hardest-ultracycling-event/","date":1780063691000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/OMM-Film-Tour-de-Frankie-hero.jpeg\" width=\"1280\" height=\"717\" alt=\"&lt;i&gt;(Photos/Paola Berber)&lt;/i&gt;\" /></p>\n<p>Today, Old Man Mountain (OMM) reached out to share a new film about their ‘<a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/old-man-mountain-experimental-bikepacking-team-announced/\" target=\"_blank\">Experimental Bikepacking Team</a>‘ member, Paola Berber (<em>aka Poli</em>), completing Le Tour de Frankie… for the third time!</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/OMM-Film-Tour-de-Frankie-sitting.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"719\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/OMM-Film-Tour-de-Frankie-sitting.jpeg\" alt=\"OMM Film Tour de Frankie sitting\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/OMM-Film-Tour-de-Frankie-sitting.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/OMM-Film-Tour-de-Frankie-sitting-297x167.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/OMM-Film-Tour-de-Frankie-sitting-120x67.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/OMM-Film-Tour-de-Frankie-sitting-768x431.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/OMM-Film-Tour-de-Frankie-sitting-1200x675.jpeg 1200w\" /></a><figcaption><em>(Photos/Paola Berber)</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>In the short film directed, edited, and produced by Poli, she explores what keeps her coming back to this grueling race time after time. I didn’t know this, but Le Tour de Frankie is Mexico’s most difficult, and arguably then most important ultracycling event.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/OMM-Film-Tour-de-Frankie-donkeys.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/OMM-Film-Tour-de-Frankie-donkeys.jpeg\" alt=\"OMM Film Tour de Frankie donkeys\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/OMM-Film-Tour-de-Frankie-donkeys.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/OMM-Film-Tour-de-Frankie-donkeys-297x167.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/OMM-Film-Tour-de-Frankie-donkeys-120x68.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/OMM-Film-Tour-de-Frankie-donkeys-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/OMM-Film-Tour-de-Frankie-donkeys-1200x675.jpeg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/OMM-Film-Tour-de-Frankie-ocean.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"712\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/OMM-Film-Tour-de-Frankie-ocean.jpeg\" alt=\"OMM Film Tour de Frankie ocean\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/OMM-Film-Tour-de-Frankie-ocean.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/OMM-Film-Tour-de-Frankie-ocean-297x165.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/OMM-Film-Tour-de-Frankie-ocean-120x67.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/OMM-Film-Tour-de-Frankie-ocean-768x427.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The movie is subtitled and filmed very well. It’s filled with amazingly beautiful scenery, and is a real pleasure to watch. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Hats off to you, Poli! </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Check it out to get hyped for the weekend…</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><div>\n\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://oldmanmountain.com/\" target=\"_blank\">OldManMountain.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/tour-de-frankie-must-see-paola-berbers-3rd-ride-of-mexicos-hardest-ultracycling-event/\">Tour de Frankie Must See: Paola Berber’s 3rd Ride of Mexico’s Hardest Ultracycling Event</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"f49d052f0869eed8e18484b9a8ea2b91e2d2c229453ba33f376f97a7a95f0234","category":"Cycling"}